org.jpws.data

Class Exchange.DataField

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jpws.data.Exchange.DataField
  • Enclosing class:
    Exchange

    public static class Exchange.DataField
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a datafield of a database record in its generic plane. Currently it only serves to identify a datafield by name. In future it might also describe generic static or variable features of datafields.
